# The frontend holds NO upstream API keys. All market data is fetched through
# the backend proxy, which keeps Alpha Vantage / Finnhub keys server-side —
# anything with a VITE_ prefix is bundled into the browser and is public.
# To configure providers, see backend/.env.example instead.

# Optional. Leave unset for local dev: vite proxies /api to the backend
# (see vite.config.ts). Set this only in production, to the deployed backend
# origin, e.g. https://api.example.com
# VITE_API_BASE=
